OL,10,GIn this talk I’ll introduce the
OL,11,Ghistory, science and art of uranium
OL,12,Gglass. It’s something that’s been
OL,13,Garound for more than a hundred years
OL,14,Gand is still made today. I’ll explain
OL,15,Ghow uranium glass gets its glow under
OL,16,GUV light, whether or not it’s safe to
OL,17,Gown (spoiler alert: absolutely safe)
OL,18,Gand why it exists in the first place.
OL,19,GI’ll explore some of the history of
OL,20,Guranium glass and its origins and I’ll
